- Rejected negative numeric send_key chain delays instead of sending them as keys and released fork version 2026.7.12.
- Added HACS validation GitHub Action and updated documentation for HACS custom repository installation.
- Updated integration manifest links for HACS validation and released fork version 2026.7.13.
